social_posts.post_text: Past weekends duck hunt was a great one! Didn’t get any birds, but a great hunt none the less! Beautiful sunsets, wood duck hole scouting, and enjoying being on the water with some buddies . #duckhunting #georgia #waterfowlhunting
Gender reveal for Memphis Miller Johnson! 🤍

I finally was able to get my hands on some @bgcornhole #sorcerers . I literally got these hours before the tournament and was able to place 3rd in a local blind draw with some of the top local guys I look up to! Keep your eyes peeled for future drops because these fly off the shelves and for good reason! #bgcornhole #baggodz #aclcornhole #blinddraw #sorcerers

Ended up taking 2nd place at yesterdays regional in intermediate doubles! Shout out to @bgcornhole for making the best bags helping me get a podium finish. ✌🏻 #bgcornhole #bgorgohome #baggodz #wizards #aclcornhole #podium

For the year of 2022 our company had a regional contest for those who performed exceptionally , built homes faster than the template, as well as customer satisfaction that was 9.8% or better per home. Out of 9 total builders in the south region my number was selected in the drawing to win this 2022 Kawasaki 310x jet ski! I am so grateful to have been drawn for this contest. #lifebuiltbetter #meritagehomes #contructionmanager

Happy Mothers Day to my beautiful wife Kailee (@raising_johnsons ) . I admire her dedication to being the best mom. I envy her patience that she has with kids and I! Kailee is nothing short of an exceptional mother and wife. I am so grateful to share a family and a life together with her 🤍. We cannot wait for Memphis Miller Johnson to be here to join our family!
#happymothersday

First solo outing on the new rig! 
#edgeduckboats #1553 #lakelanier #fishing

Took home first place in our first league with Georgia Cornhole events with my father in law and grandfather in law! Good times throwing with great people! #cornhole #georgiacornholeevents #cummingcitycenter
The kids got to run a Mini X for the first time this past weekend and they loved it! 🤍🚜

Opening day 2023. What an experience it was! From only getting about 4.5 hours of sleep all weekend, sleeping 3.5 of those hours in the boat beached on an island, hitting a submerged tree in the pitch black while running wide open trying to get to our spot, installing lights on Dave’s boat, getting duck fever and shaking in excitement after getting on my first Hen Woodie, to just hanging out and laughing with the boys. This hunt may not landed many ducks in the boat but it was filled with many memories and good times! Shout out to @dave_strickman for the invite, hospitality staying at the farm, and a damn good time! #duckhunting #openingday #edgeboats #1553 #woodduck

I am so grateful for the opportunity to partner with @webbwestern ! If you’re looking to get some last minute Christmas shopping done, click the link in my bio to check out the #webbwestern website.  My promo code is MattJ10 for 10% of your entire order!
